<h1 style="margin-top: 0; color: #333333; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; text-align: left;" align="left"><%= @provider.first_name %>, your help request has been created.</h1>
<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.625; color: #51545E; margin: .4em 0 1.1875em;">Here is a public link with your help request details to share with your friends, family, community, and local neighborhood groups.</p>
<table align='center' style='text-align:center'>
  <tr>
    <td align='center' style='text-align:center'>
<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.625; color: #51545E; margin: .4em 0 1.1875em;"><strong><a href="<%= @request_url %>"><%= @request_url %></a></strong></p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.625; color: #51545E; margin: .4em 0 1.1875em;">A HospitalHero team member will reach out to you when we've found a good volunteer match - or if we need additional info.</p>
<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.625; color: #51545E; margin: .4em 0 1.1875em;">You can edit or delete your request at any time by clicking the link below.</p>
<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.625; color: #51545E; margin: .4em 0 1.1875em;"><a href="<%= @edit_url %>"><%= @edit_url %></a></p>
<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.625; color: #51545E; margin: .4em 0 1.1875em;">Please spread the word to your colleagues and friends so we can help support everyone you work with!</p>
<table align="center" style="width: 50%">
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      <%= link_to(SocialMediaLink::FACEBOOK_LINK, target:"_blank") do %>
        <%= image_tag("facebook_icon.png") %>
      <% end %>
    </td>
    <td align="center">
      <%= link_to(SocialMediaLink::TWITTER_LINK, target:"_blank") do %>
        <%= image_tag("twitter_icon.png") %>
      <% end %>
    </td>
    <td align="center">
      <%= link_to(SocialMediaLink::LINKEDIN_LINK, target:"_blank") do %>
        <%= image_tag("linkedin_icon.png") %>
      <% end %>
    </td>
    <td align="center">
      <%= link_to(SocialMediaLink::EMAIL_LINK, target:"_blank") do %>
        <%= image_tag("email_contact_icon.png") %>
      <% end %>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.625; color: #51545E; margin: 1.1875em 0 1.1875em;">We truly appreciate your service. Please reach out to us if you have any other suggestions for other ways we can help you.</p>
<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.625; color: #51545E; margin: .4em 0 1.1875em;">Best,
<br />The HospitalHero Team</p>
